Subject: [PATCH] tracing: Fix setting of start_index in find_next()

commit f36d1be2930ede0a1947686e1126ffda5d5ee1bb upstream.

When we do cat /sys/kernel/debug/tracing/printk_formats, we hit kernel
panic at t_show.

